# Base Network Information

## What is Base?
Base is an Ethereum Layer 2 blockchain built
by Coinbase. It is fast, cheap, and secure.

## Why Base?
- Low gas fees (fractions of a cent)
- Fast transactions (2 second block time)
- Built by Coinbase — trusted and backed
- EVM compatible — all Ethereum tools work
- Growing ecosystem of apps and users

## Network details

### Base Mainnet
- Chain ID: 8453
- RPC URL: https://mainnet.base.org
- Explorer: https://basescan.org
- Symbol: ETH

### Base Sepolia (Testnet)
- Chain ID: 84532
- RPC URL: https://sepolia.base.org
- Explorer: https://sepolia.basescan.org
- Symbol: ETH (free from faucets)

## Bridging to Base
- Official bridge: bridge.base.org
- From Ethereum to Base takes ~1 minute
- From Base to Ethereum takes ~7 days
- Third-party bridges are faster for withdrawal

## Gas on Base
Average transaction costs less than $0.01.
Much cheaper than Ethereum mainnet.